{"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint"},{"type":"text","text":". Otherwise, it is ignored."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression contai